{"word":"G4662 - σκωληκόβρωτος - skōlēkóbrōtos - sko-lay-kob'-ro-tos - Eaten of worms","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">σκωληκόβρωτος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">skōlēkóbrōtos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">sko-lay-kob'-ro-tos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Eaten of worms</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"புழுப்புழுத்த - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"eaten of worms"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G4663 - σκώληξ - skṓlēx - sko'-lakes/4663\">G4663</a> and a derivative of <a href=\"#/G977 - βιβρώσκω - bibrṓskō - bib-ro'-sko/977\">G977</a>; <i>worm eaten</i>, that is, <i>diseased with maggots:</i> - eaten of worms.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G4662/4662\">G4662</a>, <a href=\"#/G4663/4663\">G4663</a>"}]}